     H            Y.
     F** AM#R35  *******************************************
     F* CAMRY PART LOOKUP FROM KANBAN#                     *
     F*      LEC.        2023.07.19                        *
     F******************************************************
     FAFFWP25 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAL#PL01NIF  E           K        DISK
     FAFFWP26 O   E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   5 CASHN1
     I                                        6  10 CASHN2
     I                                       11  12 CASHN3
     I                                        1  12 CASHN
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KANB
     C                     KFLD           NUKE
      *
      *-----------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *-----------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     READ AFFWP25                  50
      *
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           FLD2      IFNE 'Total'
      *
     C                     MOVELFLD1      KANB    4
     C                     MOVELFLD2      NUKE    4
      *
     C           KEY       CHAINAL#PL01N             51
     C           *IN51     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELCAMHN     AFMHIN
     C                     MOVELCASHN     AFSHIN
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL'N/F'     AFMHIN
     C                     MOVEL'N/F'     AFSHIN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELKANB      AFKNB#
     C                     MOVELNUKE      AFNUKE
      *
     C                     WRITEAFFWP261
     C                     CLEARAFFWP261
      *
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     READ AFFWP25                  50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
